Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.83,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.54,0:00:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.52,0:00:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.29,0:00:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.03,0:00:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.77,0:00:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.14,0:00:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.25,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.29,0:01:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.96,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.33,0:01:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.56,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#12愛情的危機!你明明說過愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,4點20分,時間應該還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙在幹嘛\N居然西裝筆挺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.26,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員跟三鷹約…約會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩張票很貴耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.55,0:03:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪本,是我啦,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空的話\N要不要一起去看個電影?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,我有票,指定席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.80,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要請我看電影嗎?\N真是難得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.20,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別傻了,誰要請你啊\N你要給我付錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?手頭緊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.71,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有女朋友的話\N我就不會打電話給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼意思!\N你這種彷佛在取笑我的笑聲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.55,0:04:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也沒資格說我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.49,0:04:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,況且我可是好心邀你出來看電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人要打電話,我掛了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是五代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道我是誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前在同一家酒店打工的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫七尾小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起來了,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對我沒什麼印象嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.76,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦,因為我都在外頭送貨\N很少在店裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我對於人名\N一向不太記得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且妳把眼鏡拿下來\N簡直變成另外一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把打工賺的錢\N拿去配了一副隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.18,0:05:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來是打算買別的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來突然買了隱形眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你猜不出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你大概也猜不出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.17,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個啊,這是電影票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇,指定席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近這部電影很受女生歡迎耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是這麼聽說\N才特地去買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好喔,我好想看這部電影喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好羨慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果妳願意的話\N要不要一起去看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思\N好像是我硬要你帶我去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.25,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說,我也正愁沒人陪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會造成你的困擾吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.20,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員和三鷹到哪裡去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,現在他們兩個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.44,0:06:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.75,0:06:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?快點走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們改走另外一條路\N走另外一條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?車站就在前面耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正走就對了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.86,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,你是五代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真…真巧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也出來約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不能小看你\N居然把手放在人家肩上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是我以前打工的同事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.26,0:07:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點走吧,電影要來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個真是速配的一對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他明明跟我說他愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻有個那麼年輕可愛的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是在捉弄我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了\N竟然玩弄女人的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.60,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,不快點的話\N我們的音樂會也要遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,再一下就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不原諒你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是在說你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好恐怖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這種電影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好沒有找管理員來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.03,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她是管理員就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(莫札特)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場音樂會好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能約妳一起來真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次請再跟我一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊,如果你願意邀我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.76,0:09:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然的\N能和妳這樣在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況,今晚妳真的好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,只有今晚而已嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好壞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他竟然有個那麼\N年輕可愛的女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.22,0:10:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,我們找個地方吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然還想辯解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太不像男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳可以喝一點酒吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要開車,所以不能喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\N我不會叫妳喝酒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.83,0:11:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好恐怖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.67,0:11:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好噁心\N看來暫時會吃不下飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然黏在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們平常都是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.42,0:11:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橫濱有個夜景很美的餐廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果妳方便的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.43,0:11:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,橫濱可能太遠了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.27,0:11:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是橫濱還是哪裡\N我都陪你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究…究竟是怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.34,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能問妳一件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳今天願意和我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.85,0:12:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是為了想去聽音樂會而已嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有其它的理由是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你在一起,我很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一能夠讓我遠離管理員工作\N鬆口氣的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬆口氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就一個男人而言呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.03,0:13:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是也有女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也?妳有男朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我不是在說我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有什麼男朋友!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以問你一件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的電影\N你原本是想跟誰去看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在路上遇見的那個女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.33,0:14:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是\N她有個很登對的男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管原本要跟誰去看\N我今天真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.21,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我在一起很無聊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會啊,妳很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好高興喔\N換了隱形眼鏡終於有了價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通過這座公園可以抄近路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常我都走商店街回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天有你陪著我\N所以我不用害怕,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定反而會更恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑,我是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼突然問這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你願意把我當女人看嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.11,0:15:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是打工的同事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.37,0:16:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能被一時的感情沖昏了頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.31,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可…可是吻一下應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我口渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,我…我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次還能見面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.78,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩是不是對我有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要嚇人好不好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼眼神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有做任何不軌的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有一瞬間曾經猶豫過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.34,0:17:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過結果我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.95,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼叫得這麼悲傷呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼,不是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員還沒回來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.56,0:17:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,都已經11點半了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.77,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.58,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,不可以逃避現實喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候喝酒最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要隨便跑進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來分擔你的不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒有什麼不安呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.51,0:19:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過說到三鷹這個男人\N手腳好像很快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊,那個眼神很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員她不會的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,管理員對這種事\N沒有什麼免疫力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是個涉世未深的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很容易被浪漫的氣氛迷住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.80,0:20:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夜霧包圍著我們幽會的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想說\N夜霧,今晚也謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.01,0:20:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.79,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要難過\N痛快喝個兩杯把一切都忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她今晚大概會外宿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾一兩次早上回來也沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊,又不是小孩子的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,喝吧\N反正今晚她也不會回來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,結果弄到這麼晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會,不過我很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.95,0:20:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以再約妳出來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.95,0:20:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.69,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次不要只為了鬆口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跌到谷底,墜入痛苦的深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.80,0:21:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追求幸福\N卻墜入痛苦的深淵裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被甩了,被甩了,被討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.74,0:21:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好借酒澆愁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.99,0:21:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請下車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.89,0:21:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也來喝一杯好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真無趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.71,0:21:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走,睡覺去,睡覺去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.11,0:21:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我!放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.45,0:22:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以去,冷靜一點,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.06,0:22:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我!放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.79,0:22:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候不能去打擾人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.34,0:22:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.70,0:22:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.11,0:22:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛的力量真偉大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.81,0:22:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.15,0:22:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以,求求你,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.52,0:22:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.63,0:22:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.69,0:22:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三鷹,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.13,0:22:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的西裝弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛,真令人失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.31,0:22:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不曉得應該說無聊呢?\N還是有趣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,三更半夜的不要發出\N那種會引人誤會的叫聲啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.61,0:23:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在期待些什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.95,0:23:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.69,0:23:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續喝,繼續喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.56,0:23:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你也進來喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.46,0:23:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.23,0:23:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.87,0:23:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為有很多女人打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.77,0:23:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且每天打,打個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.47,0:24:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回\N『萬人迷的五代?當心桃色電話!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.44,0:24:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代竟然笑瞇瞇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.08,0:24:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼嘛,那個色小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.26,0:24:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.54,0:24:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.71,0:24:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.72,0:24:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
